Personal details


Born
Carol Martha Browner
(1955-12-16) December 16, 1955 (age 61)
Miami, Florida, U.S.


Political party
Democratic


Spouse(s)
Michael Podhorzer (Divorced)
Thomas Downey (2007–present)[1]


