Carol Browner - Wikipedia






















 







Carol Browner

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Carol Browner








Director of the Office of Energy and Climate Change Policy


In office
January 22, 2009 – March 3, 2011


President
Barack Obama


Deputy
Heather Zichal


